videos.description: Jae Crowder fouls Anthony Davis while guarding him, but Crowder also gets kicked on the follow-through of Davis' shot, resulting in AD being charged with a flagrant foul 1.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (AD picks up flagrant after kicking Crowder below the belt) 2021/05/25 ESHEET

videos.headline: AD picks up flagrant after kicking Crowder below the belt

videos.description: LeBron James climbs the ladder to grab the nice pass from Anthony Davis and throw down a powerful one-handed slam to cap the Lakers' fast break.

videos.headline: AD hooks up with LeBron for the oop

videos.description: Dario Saric makes an ill-advised save straight to LeBron James, who makes his way unimpeded down the floor to throw down a thunderous dunk for the Lakers.

videos.description: Chris Paul is in his bag as he loses Dennis Schroder and slips a no-look dime between defenders to Torrey Craig for an easy uncontested flush.
